NOTICE OF ASSESSMENT LIEN
RIDGE AT BANDERA RESIDENTIAL COMMUNITY INC
File No .: 24- 342-1673
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
WHEREAS, that certain Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Ridge at Bandera Residential Community Inc
(hereinafter "Association"), recorded in/under Document No. 20150219569, Book 17556, Page 705 of the Real Property Records
of Bexar County, Texas (hereinafter "Declaration") provides for a lien against the property located at 11228 Hill Top Loop,
Helotes, TX 78023 (hereinafter "Property") for the benefit of the Association to secure the payment of assessments levied
against the Property for common expenses and fees.
WHEREAS, the Declaration provides that the Association is vested with the power to assess, collect assessments, and enforce the
lien retained against the Property.
WHEREAS, according to the Association's records, ERIK MIKAEL HEITZ AND TANIA BERENISS HEITZ, HUSBAN
AND WIFE WHOSE ADDRESS IS 11228 HILL TOP LOOP. HELOTES. TX 78023, (hereinafter "Owner," whether one or
more) is the Owner of the Property legally described as follows:
LOT 14 BLOCK 5 MISSION VIEJO UNIT 3, BEXAR COUNTY, TEXAS ACCORDING TO THE MAP
OR PLAT THEREOF RECORDED IN VOLUME 9716 PAGE 201 AND AMENDED IN VOLUME 9723,
PAGE 40, DEED AND PLAT RECORDS OF BEXAR COUNTY, TEXAS.
WHEREAS, Owner is in default in the Owner's obligations to make payments for assessments and has failed, despite demand
upon the Owner, to pay Association assessments, handling charges, and collection costs properly levied against the Property, in
the amount as of 10/08/2021 equal to $1.165.04, which amount may continue to increase.
NOW THEREFORE, the Association, acting by and through a member of its Board of Directors, its duly authorized agent,
and/or its attorney, does hereby file this Notice of Assessment Lien against the Property due to non-payment of the amounts
contained herein as of the date set forth above.
EXECUTED this 3/ day of_2 20 22
May
LAW OFFICE OF BRADY T. WYATT, III
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF DALLAS
This instrument was acknowledged before me on this 31
_ day of_May
20 , by Brady T. Wyatt, III on
behalf of the Law Office of Brady T. Wyatt, III, acting on behalf of Associa Hill Country San Antonio, the duly authorized
agent for Ridge at Bandera Residential Community Inc.
GRACIELA ITZEL JASSO
Notary Public, State of Texas
Comm. Expires 11-10-2024
Notary ID 130896155
NOTARY PUBLIC
STATE OF TEXAS
